result.notes:
Details of all current Business Rates accounts held with Colchester Borough Council.  See Downloads page to access records for individual months. 

A revaluation of all non-domestic properties in England was carried out for 2017 by the Valuation Office Agency. For further details visit https://www.gov.uk/introduction-to-business-rates/how-your-rates-are-calculated  

Personal details are omitted from this data.

Details of credits or write-ons cannot be supplied as the public interest in publishing this information is outweighed by the likelihood of prejudice to the prevention of crime.  The free availability of details of business rate credits would carry a potential risk of fraud.  This information is therefore exempted from release by Section 31(1)(a) of the Freedom of Information Act 2000.
